      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Civil news: tender opportunity for housing possession work
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Tender opens 1 December 2020 to deliver services in 2 Housing Possession Court Duty Schemes (HPCDS) and closes 5pm 21 December 2020.</p>

  </div>
</div>

